API.ADK

Class MessageStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • API.ADK.MessageStructure

  • public class MessageStructure
extends java.lang.Object
    Structure of the Message (Frame format, Message ID, Frame type, Data, Data length, Timestamp). This structure is used to retrieve a message from the receive message buffer or send a message.
    Author:
    hroesdiyono
